title: BRIEF-Eagle Bulk Shipping Taken Delivery Of M/V New London Eagle
text:
47 PM / Updated 12 minutes ago BRIEF-Eagle Bulk Shipping Taken Delivery Of M/V New London Eagle Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
Jan 9 (Reuters) - Eagle Bulk Shipping Inc: 
* EAGLE BULK SHIPPING INC - ‍HAS TAKEN DELIVERY OF ITS NEWLY ACQUIRED VESSEL, M/V NEW LONDON EAGLE, A 2015-BUILT CROWN-63 ULTRAMAX​ 
* EAGLE BULK SHIPPING INC - ‍ACQUISITION OF M/V NEW LONDON EAGLE​ HAS BEEN FUNDED BY CASH ON-HAND AND NEW DEBT OF $8.6 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
